an excellent deal!&nbsp; i won't charge you any set-up fees or anything like that.&nbsp; if you've already got your own domain name, then all you will be responsible for is the $50/year (that's about $4/month -- at this rate, you can't afford not to take advantage of it) hosting fee.&nbsp; if i have to register your domain for you, it's an additional $20/year (or $30 for two years -- a $10 savings).&nbsp; again, the rates will go up after the golden sushi hosting launches.&nbsp; this same offer will be $70/year without domain registration and $100/year with one year of domain
